com.opentok.android
Class Stream

java.lang.Object
  com.opentok.android.Stream
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Stream>
public class Stream
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Stream>

Used to describe a stream bound to an OpenTok session. The Session.Listener.onSessionReceivedStream(Stream) method notifies you of new streams in the session: 

public void onSessionReceivedStream(Stream stream) {
        Subscriber subscriber = mySession.createSubscriber(subscriberView, stream);
        subscriber.connect();
        mySubscribers.add(subscriber);
}

The Session.Listener.onSessionDroppedStream(Stream) method notifies when streams are unpublished the session.
